Invocation Name: king cobra
des:
Listen to this interactive story with a timeless lesson. 
King Cobra is a black stallion, representing the creative in you, forced into a life of drudgery, amongst the human race depicting the mundane, he rebels, to escape to the wilderness, symbolizing the release to the ultimate paradise. Listen on to see if you are with the king cobra in you and will transit on a journey to that heaven of creativity? At any point, you can say "Alexa, stop" to exit the skill.
